item.dc:creator: @Kozs Kozs
item.description:
@Kozs wrote:

[quote=“CoonHunter, post:4, topic:413841”]UFO = Unidentified Flying Object

Anything, if you think this is an alien sawser (how the fuck do I spell that word?), you are mistaken. The Germans were working on this technology many many years go, its nothing really new. Its just something that was brought in to the alienated thought because of sifi movies.

Btw, Just about see it? I am legally blind in one eye and could easily see that lol. Listen for the planes engines though, those could very well be just a regular plane.[/quote]
